      "visualKind": "shape",
      "title": "<h1>Product Requirements Document: Streamlined Mobile Registration Flow</h1><h2>1. Problem Statement</h2><p>Users are abandoning our mobile app registration process due to excessive friction and complexity. The current multi-step flow (email, password, confirmation, goals, preferences) creates significant barriers to entry, with a 38% drop-off rate during email confirmation alone. This prevents users from accessing core app features and impacts user acquisition.</p><h2>2. Goal &amp; Outcome</h2><p><strong>Goal:</strong> Simplify the registration process to increase conversion rates while maintaining security.</p><p><strong>Success Metrics:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Reduce registration abandonment rate by 50%</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Increase successful first-time registrations by 40%</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Maintain 90%+ completion rate for essential profile information</li></ol><h2>3. Target Users &amp; Use Cases</h2><p><strong>Primary Users:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">New mobile app users seeking quick access to fitness/meal content</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Users with existing social media accounts (Google, Apple, Facebook)</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Users who prefer minimal commitment before exploring features</li></ol><p><strong>Key Use Cases:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Quick registration via social login</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Basic email registration with minimal friction</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Delayed profile completion after initial access</li></ol><h2>4. Proposed Solution</h2><p><strong>Core Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\">Simplified Authentication:</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Social login integration (Google, Apple, Facebook)</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Magic link email verification as fallback</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Smart defaults for user information</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">No password requirement for social login users</li><li data-list=\"ordered\">Decoupled Registration Flow:</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Minimal required fields for initial access</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Optional goal-setting and preferences</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Progressive profile completion</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Biometric login support post-registration</li></ol><p><strong>Security Measures:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Duplicate account prevention system</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Secure social authentication handling</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Account linking capabilities</li></ol><h2>5. Out of Scope</h2><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Complex profile customization during initial registration</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Advanced preference settings</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Multiple account management</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Password recovery flow</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Custom authentication methods</li></ol><h2>6. Open Questions / Assumptions</h2><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\">Technical dependencies for social login implementation</li><li data-list=\"ordered\">Security requirements for magic link implementation</li><li data-list=\"ordered\">Data retention policy for incomplete registrations</li><li data-list=\"ordered\">Minimum required user data for core functionality</li><li data-list=\"ordered\">Timeline for biometric authentication integration</li></ol>"
    },
